a5ce0b1c725a1844aa5e62a8f9e5157f34c2a36b08a178cbdeeeedf780494e1f0934bdd9ef1bc1d96893d36879c7f513b14d8789f8cb133949a832d6f11ee2b9  fix-requires.patch"
